'From Squeak2.9alpha of 12 June 2000 [latest update: #3046] on 27 November 2000 at 1:18:45 pm'!"Change Set:		TetrisFixDate:			27 November 2000Author:			Dan IngallsTwo fixes, suggested by Andreas Raab to make Tetris compliant with the new alignment protocols."!!Tetris methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'di 11/25/2000 20:47'!initialize	super initialize.	board _ TetrisBoard new game: self.	color _ Color lightGray.	self listDirection: #topToBottom.	self wrapCentering: #center.	self vResizing: #shrinkWrap.	self hResizing: #shrinkWrap.	self layoutInset: 3.	self 		addMorphBack: self makeGameControls;		addMorphBack: self makeMovementControls;		addMorphBack: self showScoreDisplay;		addMorphBack: board.	board newGame.! !!Tetris methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'di 11/25/2000 20:52'!showScoreDisplay	^ self rowForButtons		hResizing: #shrinkWrap;		addMorph: (self wrapPanel: ((scoreDisplay _ LedMorph new) digits: 5; extent: (4*10@15)) 						label: 'Score:')! !